{"tid":2198027,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"可彎曲螢幕、柔性電池專利獲准，Apple大量採購 Samsung 柔性螢幕，摺疊iPhone最快2021問世","createTime":"2020-09-11T05:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T22:38:06.000Z","uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1430709f21ef92adea994329ee24c2719bf1499c","tid":2198027,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:08:00.000Z","msg":"　　自從三星成功推出第一款折疊式智慧型手機Galaxy Fold後，蘋果陣營是否會跟進便成為大家關注的焦點。最近科技部落客麥法登(Gregory McFadden)在他的推特上討論這個可能性，卻意外引來另一知名蘋果爆料者普羅瑟(Jon Prosser)，也間接證實了蘋果的確「正在研發」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jon_prosser/status/1271804555190296576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjon_prosser%2Fstatus%2F1271804555190296576&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fr%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=1af3150f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjon_prosser%2Fstatus%2F1271804555190296576&h=c8dfcc5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jon_prosser/status/1271804555190296576</a><br />\n<br />\n　　<a href=\"http://知名蘋果爆料網站MacRumors.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%9F%A5%E5%90%8D%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E7%88%86%E6%96%99%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99MacRumors.com&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fr%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=c89a3508\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">知名蘋果爆料網站MacRumors.com</a>也報導，爆料達人冰宇宙指 Apple 向螢幕生產商 Samsung Display 採購大量可摺疊柔性螢幕樣板。冰宇宙又指 Apple 要求 Samsung Display 能夠獨家提供一年的數量。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MacRumors/status/1304089383235018752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMacRumors%2Fstatus%2F1304089383235018752&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fr%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=1948bee2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMacRumors%2Fstatus%2F1304089383235018752&h=273b3984\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MacRumors/status/1304089383235018752</a><br />\n<br />\n　　摺疊機核心技術是在於多個互鎖齒輪組成的鉸鏈式設計轉軸，能讓兩塊螢幕靈活地操作，因此，軸承廠商的良率影響摺疊式手機的耐用程度。蘋果申請可將一個畫面成功分割呈現在兩個顯示器的聯合操作模式（joint operating mode）專利，已經被核准，蘋果已獲核准的專利是<strong><span class=\"red\">利用磁性元件來固定裝置</span></strong>，可以允許多個電子裝置上的顯示器使用感測器，做為測量或偵測邊緣相鄰的獨立操作模式，也可成功轉換聯合至另一個顯示器的操作模式，結合方向可有水平與垂直的方向。<br />\n<br />\n　　外界相信 Apple 的種種舉動，代表著他們正在研發螢幕可摺疊的 iPhone 新機。Apple 除了取得摺疊式設計專利，Apple 還同時研究柔性電池技術並獲得專利，將電芯打散放到不同區域，令電池變成可摺曲。<br />\n<br />\niFold 及 iFlip 概念圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htNMfYS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtNMfYS.jpg&h=8d5874ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/icUnyLx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FicUnyLx.png&h=52a43e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/x-dKwdunM3U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx-dKwdunM3U&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fr%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=47d5d3bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/x-dKwdunM3U</a>"},{"pid":"82860c982d9332017cbf2b4c8b091ef200d06b17","tid":2198027,"uid":22999,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:10:36.000Z","msg":"保守估計2皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80af9a8b5292194d61c37e2e7219653115f5166b","tid":2198027,"uid":196924,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:11:54.000Z","msg":"果然係咁<br />\nGalaxy Fold係俾其他廠睇嘅廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nAPPLE唔係又去返Samsung Mon Samsung RAM Samsung NAND Samsung電池下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafad58080be97fc0739e3922ac6d1fec6f30a91","tid":2198027,"uid":36906,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82860c982d9332017cbf2b4c8b091ef200d06b17","tid":2198027,"uid":22999,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:10:36.000Z","msg":"保守估計2皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:15:16.000Z","msg":"真呀 以前手機賣5-60